@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/
 
### Fetch employee specific dashboard data
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/employee/employeeId
 
### Get tickets assigned to the employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/tickets/employee/employeeId
 
### Fetch performance metrics for representatives
GET {{baseUrl}}/representatives/performance
 
### Get outage map data for visualization
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/outage-map
 
### Fetch all outages
GET {{baseUrl}}/outages
 
### Get outages by location
PUT  {{baseUrl}}/outages/location/locationId
 
### Update or delete a specific outage
DELETE  {{baseUrl}}/outages/outageId